parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ball joints can cause uneven tire wear, loose steering, and potentially lead to loss of control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Squeaking or loud noise from the front of the vehicle
especially when driving over bumps or turning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sagging of the leaf spring can cause uneven ride height, affect vehicle handling, and potentially lead to loss of control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: One side of the vehicle is lower than the other
especially when towing or carrying heavy loads.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the all-wheel drive system can cause unusual noises, vibrations, and potentially lead to loss of control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Loud grinding noise from the front of the vehicle or engine area
cloud of black smoke emitting from the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The instability of the rear end can cause loss of control, especially when driving down hills, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Rear end of the vehicle goes into a spin when driving down hills.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire tread separation can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The tire tread separates from the sidewall
the tire explodes
the vehicle becomes difficult to control
the tire feels wobbly or unstable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The spare tire falling off while driving can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if it occurs at high speeds.
symptoms: The spare tire falls off the vehicle
the spare tire is not properly secured.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities. The extended stopping distance can also increase the risk of rear-end collisions.
symptoms: The vehicle shakes or vibrates when driving at high speeds
loud noise from the front passenger side
loud noise when applying the brakes
rear wheel lock-up
and extended stopping distance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake rotors and pads can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Loud noise from the front passenger side
loud noise when applying the brakes
and extended stopping distance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Rear wheel lock-up
extended stopping distance
and loss of control.
